pr_body:
### What does Pull Request include?

I am creating the Past Visits Widget as per the ticket [MF-444](https://issues.openmrs.org/browse/MF-444). 

Design: https://app.zeplin.io/project/5f7223cfda10f94d67cec6d0/screen/60a794b319b28f2767b33c9c

pr_body:
### What does this PR include?

This PR includes multiple changes:

1. Extension created for visit summary. 
State required: `visitUuid` and `patientUuid` 
2. Extension created above used in active visit widget to show visit summary in every row by expanding it.

Demo

https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/51502471/127300382-217b110c-7433-43b8-9fb6-750363b8ba77.mp4
